<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0D1B2A" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <title>Privacy Policy — Colab Talent</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #f8fafc; color: #1e293b; line-height: 1.7; }
      .container { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px 80px; }
      header { background: #0D1B2A; padding: 20px 24px; }
      header a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; }
      header span { color: #38bdf8; }
      h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #0D1B2A; }
      .updated { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 40px; }
      h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 10px; color: #0D1B2A; }
      p { margin-bottom: 14px; color: #334155; }
      ul { margin: 0 0 14px 20px; color: #334155; }
      ul li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
      a { color: #0ea5e9; }
      footer { text-align: center; padding: 32px 24px; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <a href="/">Colab <span>Talent</span></a>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <p>Colab Talent is operated by TheColab Limited ("we", "us", "our"). We are committed to protecting your personal information in accordance with the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020.</p>

      <h2>1. What information we collect</h2>
      <p>When you register interest or create a profile on Colab Talent, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name and email address</li>
        <li>Your company name (for employers)</li>
        <li>Your professional skills and experience (for candidates)</li>
        <li>Any information you voluntarily provide in forms</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How we use your information</h2>
      <p>We use your information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Connect employers with suitable AI talent candidates</li>
        <li>Send you relevant updates about Colab Talent</li>
        <li>Improve our platform and services</li>
        <li>Respond to your enquiries</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will not sell or share your personal information with third parties except where necessary to provide our services.</p>

      <h2>3. How we store your information</h2>
      <p>Your data is stored securely on Cloudflare's infrastructure. We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from loss, misuse, or unauthorised access.</p>

      <h2>4. Your rights</h2>
      <p>Under the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020, you have the right to access and correct personal information we hold about you. To make a request, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@thecolab.ai">hello@thecolab.ai</a>.</p>

      <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We may use cookies or similar technologies to improve your experience on our site. You can control cookie settings through your browser.</p>

      <h2>6. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We'll post the updated version on this page with a revised date.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@thecolab.ai">hello@thecolab.ai</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>Colab Talent by TheColab &middot; <a href="/">Home</a> &middot; <a href="/terms">Terms of Use</a></p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
